'''Yî-kâ''' (儒家) he [[Khûng-chṳ́ ]] sṳ̂-sióng cho-vì chú-yeu nui-yùng ke yit-chak [[chet-ho̍k]] sṳ̂-sióng thí-hì, kì-yu ham-cho '''Yî-kau''' fe̍t chá '''Khûng-kau'''. Yî-kâ chet-ho̍k sia̍p-khi̍p chṳn-chhṳ, tho-tet, [[sa-fi]], to [[Tûng-â]] kok-koet chṳ̂-chûng hó-yû yáng-hióng-li̍t.

